# Netwerkconfiguratie

## R01

```cisco
enable
conf t

hostname LAB-RA04-C01-R01

interface gig0/0/1
 ip address 10.199.65.107 255.255.255.224
 no shutdown

interface gig0/0/0
 no shutdown

interface gig0/0/0.1
 encapsulation dot1Q 1
 ip address 172.17.4.1 255.255.255.240

interface gig0/0/0.2
 encapsulation dot1Q 2
 ip address 172.17.4.17 255.255.255.240
 ip helper-address 10.199.64.66

ip route 0.0.0.0 0.0.0.0 10.199.65.100

ip domain name pxl.local

username admin privilege 15 secret pxl

crypto key generate rsa
 2048

ip ssh version 2

line vty 0 4
 login local
 transport input ssh
 exit

netconf-yang

restconf

ip http server
ip http secure-server
ip http authentication local

end
write memory

show netconf-yang status
show platform software yang-management process
```

